  "description": {
    "zh": "兄弟，有空帮个忙吗？我知道这个请求有点奇怪，但我需要一些刀具、匕首之类的近战武器。我的收藏还缺几件，尤其是邪教徒经常携带的那种刀，那玩意儿可不好搞。我真的很想把这些收藏品凑齐。帮个忙吧，兄弟阿尔沙维尔会非常感激你的！",
    "en": "What's up man! Got some time to help out a brother again? This might be a strange request, but I need a few blades, knives, some melee weapons... basically. I want them for one of my collections, and I am still missing some pieces, so can I rely on you for this task?\n\nThe hooded dudes carry those poisoned daggers, but be careful with these weird people, they can be very dangerous, high end ammunition and armor I heard! You might find the other tools on some of the locals, or tourists. Out of tips here, that's everything I can tell you, good luck out there bro."
  },
